snippet.title: LONDON FIELDS Official Trailer 2018  Amber Heard  Thriller Mystery Movie
snippet.description:
Clairvoyant femme fatale Nicola Six has been living with a dark premonition of her impending death by murder. She begins a tangled love affair with three uniquely different men: one of whom she knows will be her murderer.
Director: Mathew Cullen
Writers: Roberta Hanley (screenplay by), Martin Amis (screenplay by) | 1 more credit »
Stars: Amber Heard, Gemma Chan, Theo James | See full cast & crew »
